People who have a lot of experience in life have started off the same way as everyone one else, from the bottom. Their first ever job was something that they probably had never done before, this makes it so that they had to learn and adapt to something they were unfamiliar with. Hiring these people, people who had little to no experience to what they are now are the one who went on in life by learning and adapting. Hiring new people can also benefit employers in a positive way, by having someone with no experience can help grow that person professionally. Also finding someone with a lot of knowledge at something may be difficult for they all have jobs that require experience. This in the end can make it hard for employers to find someone just right for the position they need

Hiring someone who doesn't have experience in the job position you are looking for can be a good thing, first, it can help the employee discover skills for themselves and outside of the job, second, it can or will make the employee much better and more reliable for the position. New employees need a mentor or someone who can show them the correct ways to do the job and who ever the mentor is, it can help them grow their leadership skills dramatically. Having skill diversity among the group can also be very beneficial it can result in the new employees finding new ways to manage things on the job and may even find ways to replace the old rules for better ones. Some people are fast learners so he/she will adapt to the new work environment very easily. Building up experience is a key part in life and and some point there will be a time to get a job and seeing that everyone has started from the bottom, and hiring someone new can really benefit the company and the employer

Do i think that employers should hire someone that doesn't have any experience at something; yes, once hiring he/she the employee will do whatever it takes to keep that job and find new ways to grow while on the job. it is also a good way to expand company diversity and skills.

In the end, anyone who is looking for a job should be given an opportunity to learn and acquire skills to become better and stronger experience wise. Employers should mostly take notice on how ready and determined he/she is for the job rather than hoe much experience they have. At some point even the employer was given a chance so whoever the person may be should also be given a chance at this opportunity. I hope you take this letter into consideration and offer positions to someone who is eager to learn and be part of your group.

sincerely

The question I have been asked the most is " What do you want to be when you grow up." Lots of people ask me that question because I am a junior, but I am still deciding on what I want to be. Some people may think choosing a career at a young age is a great idea, but in reality it really is not a good idea. Committing to a career at a young age is not the best idea because they are to focus on their future that they don't see what is going on in their life's, also it is bad for your health, and kids might change their minds.

I see too many children and teenagers focusing on their future way too much that they don't have time to see life. Its better to enjoy life now at a young age then later at a much older age. Kids, children, and young students should be outside playing with dolls or toys not worrying about their careers. In addition, some people don't have time to be with their own families because they're choosing their careers.

Scientists say " That worrying about careers and the future is really bad for your health." You are thinking to much about your future that you get headaches when you think. Often in times, you have to many applications to do or to much homework that you don't get enough sleep. For example, I am a junior this year, sometimes I stare at a computer to much because of college applications;

when I am done my eyes start to hurt really bad.

We like to change our minds a lot when we are little. Children might say "I like this or that", but when they grow up and get more mature; that is a different story. When i was a little girl I would always say " I want to be a secretary" ,but now I want to be an accountant. We as people will not always like the same things we use to like when we were little.

As you have read, in this passage, focusing on our careers at a young age is not the most important thing in our lives at that moment. Only when we realizes that life is to short; we will stop asking "what do you want to be when you grow up."As a result, we should let kids be kids and adults be adults.

full_text:
BENEFITS OF A FOUR-DAY SCHOOL WEEK

Getting enough sleep is one of the best thing one could ever have! This is equivalent to having an extra day off at work or school. Therefore, schools should adopt the habit of a four-day school week by extending the school day two hours. The benefits of changing to a four-day school week, conserves energy and resources, improves academic performances and provides enough time to complete school assignments.

The amount of energy and resources used at school for a whole week is more than what we use at home. An example of such is electricity and water. The more we use, the more the school pays for it. That one extra day off reduces expenses in respect of food services,transportation and utilities.

Not only does the school conserves energy and resources, but also offers teachers and students an additional day for rest every week. As a result of that, there is less stress over school works. Students feel less pressured because they have enough rest at home before coming to school. This is an important factor that helps improve the academic performances of students.

Notwithstanding the fact that, the school conserves energy and resources, and provides enough rest, students will also have enough time to complete their assignments. Most students complain they do not get time at home, to finish up with the homework given to them by their teachers. When this continuously happens, it could drop down their grades. Having an additional day, making it three-day weekend instead of two, will give them more time to prepare for tests and study at their own pace.

Switching to a four-day school week will help change a lot. It would have a positive effect on the school, students and as well as the parents.

My school should follow the four-day week school model. It would help students to get more free time to do any school work that they could not finish during school or any other thing they would like to do. It would help many students that work during the weekends; by given students a free day off a five-day school week, can help them to finish any school work that they could not finish during the school week.

To begin, students like me that would like to learn different things out of school, for example: boxing, drawing, singing or just to get better in yours skills can get a good benefit of this four-day school week model. To be honest, it could help me a lot too. I always like to try or learn new things and I know many other students like me that would like to learn new things out of school. Like me for example, I like boxing, but I cannot practice it at school. By given us a four-day school week; I would have some time to practicing in my skills and get better at anything that I wish do get better and not just me, I have friends that like to draw, but they do not practice it because they dont have time, because they work which means they only got time to get their homework done.

For intense, students that works during the weekends by given them an extra day off to do what they cannot do in the weeks days would help them.

In fact, students that work during week days can help them a lot too. Following this model in school, teachers or any school worker can be beneficial for them too, because they can get more time to expend with their families or they can use this time to revise students work.

Expending the school day two hours can cause some students to increase their stress or anxiety; students that don't like school can try to skip some hours, which means the security have to improve their methods to stop students from skipping classes.

Is it a good idea for students to finish high school in three years and entire collage? People have different opinion about that. Some people believe it is a good idea for students to finish high school in three years. However, I believe it is not a good idea for students to finish high school in three years and entire collage, because most of the students do not get enough mature education from the high school , they lost the normal student life, and most of the students' future affected by this decision.

Most of the students do not get enough mature education from the high school. Most of the students who finish high school in three years, basically, they have the shaky education skills.

If students want to finish high school early, then they do not have opportunity to learn some extra courses beside their necessary courses such as some extra AP classes, and some electives. Also, they are not able join school's extracariculam activities like some important clubs. such as National English Honor Socity, National Science Honor society, etc for lack their of the time. Some of these extra important activities and classes may give them much knowledge to do better in collage that they couldn't get out early from the high school. That's why students do not get enough mature from the high school education.

Students lost the normal student life. They have to rush to finish high school early, so they have to finish lot of things in a short time. They have to take all normal classes, and also the class in the evening. They have to take the class in summer, so they couldn't enjoy the summer with family and friends. Also, some of the students not able to take the enjoyable elective courses like PE, music, and art for their rush to finish high school early. Sometimes, they get frustrated on their life. Basically, they couldn't enjoy the beautiful student life like other normal high school students. That's why student's lost their normal student life.

Most of the students' future affected by this decision. Sometimes, they maxed out everything to rush for get out early from the high school. Students have lot of test in a same time, but they do not have enough time to prepare well for all the tests. For that, most of the students do not get good grades and most of them do not get the main function of the subject. As a result to finish high school early and do not understand the main concept of high school's subjects, so they need much more time to understand the higher lever collage subjects, and take long time to finish the collage. Most of the students life get more complected way than they thought, for that unnessery rush in a wrong time. Most of the students face diffelticulties to reach their dream carriers. That's why most of the students' future affected by this decision.

In conclusion, it is not a good idea for students to finish high school in three years and entire collage. Student should not finish high school in three years, because most of the students do not get enough mature from the high school education, they lost the normal student life, and most of the students' future affected by this decision. Most of them think they are advanced in one year, but most of them actually behind one year. Without this four years in high school students are not well prepare for their beautiful future.

full_text:
Summer is the time for students to take a break from school, but some educators feel that summer break is too long and it needs to be shorten. As for me, I am strongly disagree with this idea because summer is the time for student to visit their famiy, their relatives, to do whatever they like, to enjoy whatever they love and sometimes learning too much might be somthing that some students could not handle.

First of all, summer is the time for students to come back to their hometown to visit their family. Some students, like me, came from another country so a lot of times we do miss our hometown. That is why having a three month summer break is truly a huge chance for us because that is pretty much the only reunion we have in a year. I will take mine as an example. To be able to come back to Generic_City it is not just about time, sometimes it could involve money. The ticket is just too expensive, not to mention that it is in summer. So if I can visit my family this year, I might have to wait a few years later to be able to visit them again.

Secondly, this is a period of time where students can do whatever thay want to do like doing some volunteering or club activities or playing sports or just simply doing their favorite hobbies. If we shorten the summer break, students will easily get bored when they come back to school because they do not have enough time to do what they like in summer. Nobody wants to study when they are bored. So if we want a student to return to school with lots of energy, we need to let them have a break. And that give me an example. One of my Vietnamese friend told me that even in summer he still have to take a lot of tutor classes. That is why if we shorten the summer break then lots and lots of Asian students will not even have time to do what they love!

Last but not least, learning too much might be something that some students could not handle. A short summer break meaning we have to go to school more than we need. I know that if we shorten the summer break we will have a longer winter break, but that is not the case for the country that does not have a winter break or a week off in fall and spring. A student could get stress if they do not have a proper break. Just check some examples on the news or internet, especially in South Korea or Japan. A lot of students suicide just because of learning too much. Too many homeworks and tests, pressures from parents and teacher,.... Very stressful! Not to mention that Asian students usually have a shorter summer break and winter break.

On the whole, I am not agree with this idea and along with fact that I am an Asian and I used to go through a very strict and tough education in Asia, I can never accept this. Students need to have some times to release their stress after a long year at school by visiting their family or doing whatever they like.

As much as I love being lazy, I support the fact that everyone should be active all the time. Some might say having some rest is good, but too much rest is not good all the time. The phrase "being active" has different meaning for different types of people, as of for me I define it as studying or doing my homework or even doing my chores but for some people it might be doing their jobs or researching or even helping out others.

Being active has changed as time changed, long before technology a lot of people worked actively, they didn't have social Medea, phones, computers or even emails, they did everything hand by hand but nowadays almost everyone sites at home and let technology takes control, this has both bad and good effect but the bad side takes the majority effect. These bad effects brought health problems like; obesity, diabetics and so on. Being active can also be working out.

I believe, if someone works actively towards achieving their goals, they can accomplish anything they want(if it is realistic of course). We can see some famous scientist like Albert Einstein, Stephen Hawkins and Thomas Edison that worked day and night to prove something for the society and I believe these people changed the way that we are living right now.

Having said all this I am such a lazy person that completely agrees with what Thomas Jefferson wrote, so in conclusion, please don't be lazy all the time think about your future, your health and things that you can accomplish so get up and be active.

Should students graduate from High School early? In the actuality, there are so many cases where students at the age of 17 years old are graduating early. Few of them gets tired, or even bored to study. In the other hand, most of those students thinks that it is an efective idea of taken a whole year off, by working hard to pay their own bills, or even saving money to pay their studies. But, it is not the "best"option either. Students should not graduate early from High School because they do not accelerate their life, grow their knowledege, and plan their future.

To begin, through this period of time, students used to think about finishing High school as soon as possible. At this point, students should realized that everything takes time. Why do they accelerate their life? Why do they have to rush their education? I believe that students should complete their four years of High School, since, they are going to be able to think about what they really want to study. Decide just for one career to study in college it is not that easy. For example, a student had been thinking about study engineer his whole life. But, at the end, he found out a hobby that became his passion. So, that student has not a clear idea about what career he should choose, and which college he should applied. That's why that student will find out through this four years which option will be benefit for his future. In additon, each student will be capable to make an efective decision without any regret.

Second of all, students will have the capacity of growing up their knowledge. Since, each day they get to learn new topics from their teachers. Which is efective, because it is going to be worthy for college, since, its homework is more explicit, and extense. It is the opposite from high school. But, if students gets everything what they had learn in high school, it is not going to affect them at all.

Most of them, exploit this four years of high school to organizing their ideas. I believe that it is efective to have a clear perspective, nor mentallity of what you want to become in your new stage of your life.

For example, looking,and applying for schoolarships, since, some students do not have enough money to pay it. Also, they are able to planify their future by limiting their "wants", since, paying a college, here in the U.S., it is expensive. Furthermore, students start being mature, and use to be more responsible, since, they already know what they really need in their own life to succeed.

In conclusion, students should complete their high school without rushing. Of the fact of getting knowledge from teachers is benefitial, since each day we learn new things. And, being organize with your schedule, planify your ideas. It will be helpful on the career you choose. You will succeed, if you take your time by not accelerate to do not take inadequates decisions that you will regret it.

Someone who is constantly doing something can accomplish more? Or does inactivity also serve a purpose? This brings me back to my middle school days, where I was failing math class. Everyday I was lazy to study. Falling asleep in class and not taking notes really wasn't the best idea. After, home from school I would not bother doing my homework. A few weeks have gone by and my grade was going downhill. I was shocked I've gotten an F but not surprised. Sitting around and doing nothing was definitely not going to get me anywhere. Bringing up the grade was the first thing I had to do. My professor Generic_Name gave me advice, she told me to practice and study. Her advice helped me improve. Weeks later, my grade went up to a B, I couldn't be any happier. Sometimes an inactive person may still accomplish something but doesn't mean we shouldn't be active people. For example, my 16 year old cousin Generic_Name on the basketball team in his high school, always missed his basketball practices and wouldn't work out, yet his team would always win games. Eventhough, inactivity can still lead you to accomplishments, being active all the time will get you further than others because more tasks may be done, you'll stay motivated, and more opportunities will be available to you.

First of all, when you get a job, your boss will not hire you if you seem like a very lazy person. Someone with a very inactive life will be seen as unmotivated and will not take the job seriously. For instance, my mom a former cook at a Mexican restaurant, once came home very tired I asked her why was she looked unhappy, her reply was that no one at work gets anything done,they ignore the boss, use their cellphones and don't know how to take orders. Therefore, she gets payed extra because she takes her job more serious than her coworkers. She told me that when I get a job not to fall in their footsteps and to stay on task because I would get fired. It really isn't as hard as you might think when it comes to completing something, the more you do the better the chances you are to accomplish.

Secondly, by even just trying and doing something, we learn more than those who decide to just give up and sit around. Sometimes we have to push ourselves to do more than we think we can. Our minds tell us we can't do it but in reality we can achieve great things but you need to know that it's not going to happen out of the blue. There is no purpose in accomplishing without doing something to get there. Determining to stay active is something we will need to consider for the rest of our lives. Inactivity never serves a purpose to us because it keeps us from achieving wonderful things in life.

Although, many people get away with their unmotivation and still get somewhere, it has no meaning. But does that mean we should just not try at all and expect to get things done? Absolutely not, never listen to those who say that because that will make you lose motivation. Overall, we are capable of achieving more by doing something than those who don't because we will have a greater chance of getting our work done, we won't get lazy, and we'll have more jobs and offers loaned to us.

All this persons have something in common ,the way how they reached their goals, fighting against any adversity. we have the case of one of the best bands in the history, The Beatles how they were rejected and some people said they didn't have a chance in the industry of music , but they kept trying, and they accomplish their goal; now they are in the history of music.

Strong and smart people know that nothing comes easy, meaning we have to give the best of us to accomplish what we want. People tend to think that setting a goal high to achieve is a smart idea. While the other side thinks that setting a goal low is the better. Although some people may hate setting a goal high and falling short, it can cause a person to give up, but they forget to neglect the part that goals or achievements come in different shapes and sizes. People should be aiming their achievements high because people can achieve more, people can feel more motivated, and people can feel more successful.

Some people may not agree with this position because setting a goal to high and then falling short can cause a person to feel less motivated. they believe this because when setting a goal high and it fails, it can make a person give up and not try. they may think this because when giving up on a goal it can cause a person to feel empty and wanting to not try again. this shows that some people are afraid of failing, and when they do fail it makes them not try again. However, the oppositions looks over other important points.

People should be aiming their achievements high so they can achieve more. when a person sets their goal high, it could mean they are setting multiple goals and not just one, having one goal is great, but having multiple is also fantastic. this can also make the person feel good about themselves, knowing that they have accomplished more than one achievement. it can also make them feel proud about themselves. Even if a person failed one goal that doesn't mean they can't accomplish other goals. People cannot accomplish every goal, all goals are different then one another, but other harder goals can be accomplished.

people should be aiming their achievement high because it can make a person feel more successful. Once a person has completed an achievement it can make them as if they succeeded. it can also help with their confidence, it would give them less anxiety. it also shows that the person who is working towards his or her achievement can do so much more. it can also help some people in the future because they have the confidence they need because they hit different goals. people can also feel like they did something with their life and not feel like they did not accomplish anything in life.

People should aim their achievements high because they can feel more motivated. Setting an achievement means working really hard. It means you must focus on, it should be the only thing you are working on. Most people in their mind focus on this and this is what motivates them to work on one persons goal. In their brain they get this sense of energy, their brain is telling them to work on their goal. that is what make some people want to work towards their goal or try to finish their goal.

Firts example, one reason that why I agree with this statement is because,if you want to apply for a job, you need to have a positive attitude to be sucessful for other people because they want to see the best of you and if you can have that job and how you relate with other people and you will see the results about it . Many people with bad attitude are lay off of their work because at work you have to show your best attitude with the costumers,boss or with other workers but some people don't do it . If you are the boss, you needs to have a positive attitude or try to have it because your workers hope the best attitude of you to manage the job and that can show respect of your person.

Second example, another reason that why I agree with this statement is because all people desserve positive attitude like, if you are walking at the park and you say "hi" or "have a good day" to other person with a positive actitude they will feel good and they would think that you are a good person . Be a person with a positive attitude can be successful for yourself or for your family for example, if one of the family members has a bad day and they see you, his mood can change because of your positive attitude, you make him feel better with advices about how he needs many options to resolve his life but if you have a bad attitude you make him feel irate of you.

Third example, the last reason that why I agree with this statement is because, if you are in the school there are many teenager like you that have hard classes, but some of them have a positive attitude because they want to have a good grades, pay attention in class and try to help other students who needs it, they try to make them sucessful too, so they can have a good grades or a good future . But, if they have a bad attitude they would be have bad grades,they don't pay attention in class,they try to distract the students who want to pay attention,make argument about the class or sometimes they scape the class because they feel that they have a bad attitude and that's why it has been said that a positive attitude is the key to success in life.

In conclusion,in this three examples I give reasons that why I agree or desagree with the statement "It has been said that a positive attitude is the key to success in life". If you have a positive attitude that can make you a better person or successful for yourself and other people.

Many students like to spend time with their friends in the school. Specially high schools are good places for students to learn and get fun with their friends. By the way some students are coming to school just for the pass their classes and work hard to graduate with high grades. I think graduate in three years instead of the traditional four years from a high school would be good for these students. Because they can go to college/university early, or work 1 year full time in a job to save money after graduated from high school or get more time to think about their career desicion.

First of all a student who graduated from high school in three years can attend to a college early. This means this student also can graduate one year early from the college and start his career early. If this student already decided to which college or university that he wants to go and what career he wants to do, this can be good for him. Also, student can understand how college classes are.

Second reason for to choose graduate early is save money for college/university. Some students who graduated from high school don't go to college/university directly. These students choose to work in a job one or two years full time to save money for college/university. This is a good option for the students who doesn't have money to pay for college/university or who doesn't want to be dependent to his family. Some families don't have money to pay their childrens' school. In this kind of situations students choose to wait one or two years instead of go to college/university directly.

Another reason to graduate early from high school is to get a extra year to make a desicion about career and college/university. Some students think it is hard to choose the right career for them in high school because when they graduateded from university their careers is going to be their whole life. Like an example sometimes students choose the job according to the classes that they liked in their high school but after they go to college/university they understand this career is not interesting more to them. According to the scientistists 35% of the college/university students decide to change their career in their freshman or sophomore year in the university. This shows that students need to think carefully while they make a decision about their careers. Also the career that a student choose effects the college/university that he wants to go because many students choose the university that gives good education and opportunites to this students about their careers that they choosed.

In conclusion I think graduate one year early from high school is a good idea for the students who wants to go to college/university early. Another reason is save money to pay college/university and final reason is to get a extra time to make a desicion about right career and school. I believe also to study and get prepared better for SAT

to get a higher score can be an extra reason. Graduate early from high school is a good idea but also can be hard for all students. So, student who wants to graduate early from high school needs to work hard.

full_text:
How technology have a positive effect on our lives? Nowadays over a billion people use different type of technology for example phones,laptops,computers, and tabs. Technology made our lives more easier than before. Although we spend most of the time using technology rather than doing physical activities,because we can read books,watch movies, play games,or shop online,it also helps in our education, and we can stay in touch with others.

Technology helps us to stay in touch with our friends and family. Through social media,we can share our daily routines,share our pictures or we can make new friends. People on social media are so excited to share their stories with others. We can learn some lessons by knowing each others experience. By sharing our lives personal experience maybe those inspires to other and they could make their lives better.

Nowadays technology have a big hand in education. Schools,Colleges,and University prefer laptops or computers more rather than using books or papers. Through technology students can easily access to their assignments or missing work. Students can take help from internet in their assignments and can easily submit their assignments to teachers online. Teachers can also access to other teachers resources to help them in teaching.

Most of the people use technology for entertainment to watch movies,play games and read books in free time. Nowadays we can play games with our friends even though they lives in other country. For entertainment we can record ourselves and upload that online as a daily v log and this is not just entertainment we can earn money through technology. We can also shop online or we can also sell products online and make money. Most of the people who are busy in their lives they prefer to shop online not going to market and search for their desire products.

We spend our most of the time using technology,for example using social media,playing games,or watching movies that leads us to get lazy,sleepy,and sometimes it feels sick. Technology is addicting we cant spend our day without using technology because technology is playing a big role in our lives. It brings so much to our lives for example entertainment, helping hand in education,and more.

Technology have some negative and positive effects on our lives but there are more positive points than negative ones. There are many helpful factors in technology that helps in our lives. Before technology life was hard to connect with people,but now you can easily call them and talk to them no matter where they live. Some negative points like we get addicted to one thing we and we spend our most of the time using it ,but there are some positive effects like it helps in education and we can earn money through technology.

The one place I would like to visit in the world would be Puerto Rico. I would like to visit Puerto Rico because of the of the beautiful weather. I would like to visit Puerto Rico because of the beautiful beach's and rivers. One other reason would be because of my family.

First, the weather most of the time is hot even in the winter is hot. In the summer sometimes is ,so hot that it can reach the temperature of 100 degrees. Most of the people living in Puerto Rico are use to the hot temperature.

Next, you would see people in the beach's or at the river some people have pool but some people can't buy pools because some don't have money and some people do have money so when the weather is hot you will see most of the people at the beach's or rivers. I personally like going to the river's because the water is colder and is really refreshing when it's really hot.

Next, another reason why I pick Puerto Rico was because of there delicious foods there a lot of tropical dishes there is something call the three meat sandwich witch is made of really tender pork meat,chicken,beef then they put potato sticks and then they add the mayo and ketchup. In the holidays like Christmas puertorican people cook a hole pig and then when the pig is done cooking they cut the pig and shred it into pieces and then they eat it with rice mix with beans.

Finally, most of my family is from Puerto Rico so most of my family know's the best places to go and the type of food that we would like. Most of are family makes a party when we come from the U.S because we only go and visit in the summer because of school we can't visit when ever we want to. When ever I visit Puerto Rico I have to see my two little brothers and my friend that I have not seen sense last summer most of the time I go to my consents house because we always play baseball or basketball ,but when it's to hot we stay home watching T.V or playing PlayStation we play with my friend that lives in Virginia. When is time to go back to the U.S are family get's sad and starst crying but we tell them that we will be back.

It is hard to think that the more effective way to be accomplish is being busy and always doing sometime. Although some people say that we accomplish more when we are inactive than when we are always doing something because we have more time to set our goals, actually we accomplish more when we are always doing something because we have more time to keep working on our goals to achieve them soon and we don't waste time that can be used to work on our goals.

Some people say that we accomplish more when we are inactive than when we are always doing something because we have more time to set our goals. The main reason why those people say that inactivity serve an important purpose is because they get more time to think what they want to do in their life and have their goals already planned. According to the New York times the people who take a moment of inactivity usually they are confident and sure about what they want to make in their life, and what goals they want to set and achieve. In addition they are more motivated and they effort more at they goals..

We accomplish more when we are always doing something because we have more time to keep working on our goals to achieve them soon. Being always active and working is the best way to achieve our goals. According to a study of the Generic_School, all the people that now is successful, they always were working on their goals and never had a moment where they thought that they had to stop and wait because the accomplishment was about to come. We always have to be working, our goals never will come easily. While we keep working on our goals, they will came to us soon.

We accomplish more when we are always doing something because we don't waste time that can be used to work on our goals. Sometimes when we are working hard on our goals, there's a time where we think that we have to stop and rest, but we shouldn't do that because that would be a waste of time that would be used to keep working. The right person to say that is my dad, when he was a teenager and already graduated, he wanted to become an Industrial Engineer, but he didn't want to go collage after he graduated. He wanted to wait and be inactive at least one year before to enter in collage, but that was a big mistake because at that time he didn't get a job, so he used a part of the money that he would have used in collage. Now he is not a Industrial Engineer, he never achieved his goal because he wasted the time that he could use to achieve his goal.

Though some people say that inactivity is more effective than activity to be accomplish because is a better way to set our goals, activity is the best way to be accomplish because we can achieve our goals more soon and we don't waste useful time. In conclusion, as you can see inactivity will not be the best way because the reality is that if we can done our goals and get a lot of wonderful things just being always active. Stop and have a good moment of relaxing might be awesome, but nothing like have what you want in our life and done things that will show out our effort and dedication.

Some schools use cell phones in the classroom for educational purposes as a helpful tool for students to study, but it turn out to be a huge problem that our school deal with. Schools purpose from letting students have and use their cell phones in class is to help them understand some hard questions or to find some definitions or anything else that help them to be successful. What makes using cell phones in the classroom a great issue are using phones in a wrong way, phones can easily distract anyone not just students, and students use it for another things, for the affections that can led students to fail their classes.

Although some schools let students use their cell phone in the classroom for educational purposes, students use their phone in a bad way by cheating or copy answers. We as students want to use the easy way to find answer without even think of the consequences of what we are about to do. I know someone from my classroom who always get caught by teacher cheating on a test or cheating on something else. To solve this problem teacher must collect phones every class to avoid students from cheating and let them have it whenever the teacher give students project that need cell phone to do. Some countries in Asia do not allow students to have their cell phone in the classroom nor school and they're really successful.

Electronic devise (cell phones) made to notify the holder if someone text him by a tone or flash light, and that work with the human Brian to make us look at it as soon as someone text us. most of us as students can't control ourselves, we want to know who send it and what he send, and that make us concentrate more on our phones and lose focusing on the class. Most of the time I can can control myself to avoid looking on my cell phone when someone text me however, since I know that's someone text me, my attention goes to my phone because I'm in class thinking on who send me and what he send. I repeat, to solve this problem teachers have to collect phones from students in the beginning of every class.

Finally, students use their cell phone for another things. Almost all students open social media (Facebook, Snapchat, etc...) while they're in a middle of a lesson, other students play games, other text on their phones, or other doing anything else. The reason why students use their cell phone is because students get bored of class for whatever reason or anything else. I remembered that guy Generic_Name, he was really smart guy, and one day our teacher give us prompt to write about, he was sitting opening Facebook for the whole class time. For all teachers I repeat for the third time collect phones from the students in the beginning of every class to avoid us from wasting times and to finishing or work.

In concussion, some schools use cell phones in the classroom for educational purposes, but we us students do the opposite thing. Most of us use cell phones for texting, games, cheating, and checking social media, and that turn out of control. If teachers didn't do anything through this issue, bad things will happen, so what will you do to stop this problem?

The life is being more modern, people also need to improve themselves. That's why some schools want to offer some programs which are good for students. Some school districts offer programs that allow high school students to graduate in three years instead of the traditional four years. Most students who allow this plan must take courses during the summers or in the evenings or may not be able to take elective courses.

This plan has two positions,some people agree, but others don't think it's a good idea. Is it a good idea? It is. It is a good idea for students to finish high school in three years and enter college or the work force one year early if the students want because they can save time, they can have new experiences, new challenges which help for their life in the future, they still can take elective courses also have vacations latter after college or work if they want.

Let's start with the first reason now. Do you agree that the time is limit? The time is the only thing you can't move back. Because of this, a lot of people, especially students are thinking how to spend time helpful. These programs will help many students save time. They can save one year in school, that also means they can reach success early one year. Many people spend summer having vacations to relax, and evenings watching TV, but the other people spend this time studying. They choose have more time after success instead of have time when they haven't had anything.

The next reason will be the reason help students the most. Most students who follow this plan will have a lot of experiences also challenges because they must have the same knowledge in shorter time than, they will have pressure, but it will grow up ourselves. They can become stronger, independent by working on own and have more information about lessons because this time is not enough for teachers can teach everything, they must research more.

The last reason refers to elective courses. Many students like these courses, but some students don't. These programs do not require to take elective courses, so some students can skip these course which they don't like or do not helpful for their career. They also take these courses after college or work if they want. They can choose also consider what is they need. Moreover, this plan don't require you skip these elective courses, you just may not be able to take these, so if you want to take courses, you can plan for this. It depends on your choice.

On the other hand, many students do not agree this plan. They think it gives stressful for them, they worry about they cannot have enough lessons. But if you think that it means you don't confide your ability also don't try for your future. Sometimes, the life needs challenges to grow up and it will be interesting. To enter college or the work, all we need are knowledge or skill, not how long we took them. You can choose your way, success will come soon or later depends on you.

Conclusion, we should support some schools offer these programs that allow high school students to graduate early if they can. Our life will change if we change, our success will come if we try, and it will happen early if we have a plan. After all, which one do you agree with? It is a challenge but many students can do. However, it will be fair if students can choose take or not these programs.

First, people can do better things. For example, my cousin Generic_Name had a soccer game at Generic_City, she and her team was talking about how they will need to play on the field, they needed to play better than the other games because the team that she was going to play against is one of the best teams that plays on that field and also her team needed to have more goals scores to keep being on the list so the can win the championship, so when they started to play they was playing like they planned it before the game and at the end of the game they won and everyone was happy because they never thought that they was going to have the chance to win that team, but they never give up.

In conclusion, I believe that going to failure to failure will not loss the enthusiasm, at the same time it could be one of the betters reasons by making people do things better, make people have a better future, and also people can feel positive by them self.

full_text:
Do you think extracurricular activities distract students? Some people think that schools should take the control of the activities students take, because extracurricular activities take students' time and energy away which makes them have little time to study or do a homework. Other people think that students should control the activities they are taking themselves because they know better their abilities and needs. I believe that giving the decision to the student is better because students know their schedule, the activities they need and their capacity.

Most of students have their own calender that they make their schedule in and put down their chores and responsibilities for each day. According to the their schedule, they choose the activities they need. In my sophomore year my math teacher required me to take an extra math class after school on Fridays. Despite it was so hard for me to stay after school and go to the basketball practice I have every Saturday tired, I was also being late to the mosque or sometimes found no energy to go. If

I was scheduling this I would choose another day in the week to practice my math as my teacher want. Since the schools or the teachers dont know student's schedule, it will be better to give the students the chance to make their own schedule.

Additionally, each student have a dream career that they want to major in. The purpose of the extracurricular activities sometimes be practicing the major students are interested in, which I think it's more important for students to practice their career than doing a homework, because it will give them the skills and the experience they will need when they graduate and major in the field they want. If schools will be choosing the activities for students, they may choose something the students are not interested in. According to an article I read about the volunteering requirements in schools, its wrong for the students to volunteer or work on something they are not interested in, this confuse them in the future while choosing a career, and this actually what happened to my brother while he was enrolling in college. He entered undecided because he did the activities the school choosed for him which was not in his interest. that's means that schools should not choose activities for students because students knows what they need and if they dont they will asks for help.

Furthermore, people born with different skills and capacity. Students know how much activity they can take. Schools sometimes give all the students the same load while not all of students can handle the same load. The school required our English class with some after school activities, which was so much for some students and while others was success others was failing. schools should let students choose the amount of the activities they need and in case if school found that the activities is so much or so low and that is effecting the their progress in school, school can contact their parents and find a solution.

Since the purpose of the school is to teach students and give them the enough knowledge to face the society, students should learn taking their own decisions and always know what better for themselves. Schools should let students choose their own activities because they best knows their schedule or responsibilities, what they want to choose to experience in, and how much load they can handle.

full_text:
First impression are very important when you first meet someone. Many people say first impressions are almost impossible to change, but i strongly disagree with that. Majority of the time when we meet someone we already think of them in a certain way, but our judgment could always be wrong. Thats why i believe first impressions could always change.

I believe that first impressions can change the way people think of you. Sometimes people can be irritable or just in a really bad mood because something is occurring in their lives, but in reality that's not how they really are. One reason first impressions can be wrong, is because maybe they didn't get enough sleep at night, and they have to get up early to go to work, or school in the morning. For example, i am not much of a morning person, so when i wake up in the mornings i can be rude, and people might not want to talk to me, but if you see me later in the afternoon i will be smiling, and laughing. Another reason first impressions could be wrong, is because they might not feel comfortable with the people who they are surrounded by, and be very shy, but once you start talking to them they change. For example, my best friend and i used to hate each other. I used to think she was annoying, and rude, and i am guessing she thought the same for me. One day we both started to talk to each other, and i found out we have many things in common, and that we are like the same people. That same day we became the best of friends, now we are basically like sisters. This is why i think that first impressions can always change.

In conclusion, i believe that from now on as we move forwards in life we shouldn't assume what the other person is like, and not to always rely on first impressions because they could always be wrong.

full_text:
Working idenpendently is harder than working as a group, but it's also better to learn things. Etheir working as a group or not you are still getting work done, and learning as you go. When I state that you can "learn" it means that you can find out things especially as a group where everyone has they're own ideas and facts about topics. Some people just take working as a group as an advantage to just copy and get answers just to get things done. Copying others does not help you learn anything other then getting your work completed.

I think it is better working alone beacuse it would be better for me to learn. Yes, i'd probably take a long time getting it done just because I would be taking my time finding little details. Some people choose not to work independently but I do. One reason why I think it is better to work alone is because of the fact that after your done you'll feel relieved and happy. If you did what you had to do alone without anybodys help besides the person who gave you the assignment, or job whatever than you done a good job just by doing your work independently.

Working as a group isn't bad I just suggest it should be better for students or anyone to work idependently also to learn what their doing instead of just getting it done when you can learn and get it done. Some people end up just copying off someone else to get stuff done. Others they actually do it and share with others who actually also have stuff done to share. Not everyone copies, nor cheats just alot of people such as students take working as a group an advantage to copy. Working together as a group can be much more easier than alone but still working independently is much more helpful for your learning benifits.

Anyone who is not used to doing independent work gets a little kick on working alone because their so used to working as a group. It helps people push them selves on finding more details, facts, and clues for what they need. If you do struggle of course you can obvisouly ask a teacher or anyone for a hand in help because you could be stuck on something. You can focus more on your work while your alone because if your in a group working it gets you distracted. If you hear other students or people talking to you, and the rest of the group giving each other ideas while your focued to find your own ideas gets you to unfocused.

Somebody elses ideas in the group could be wrong, and when you write them and use those ideas you could be wrong as well. People usually rely on others to get answers which is not right. Also it's hard for others to communicate with others as a group which it also makes it better for anyone to work alone. You could do things your own way while working independently. All of the things I wrote about help show that it is better to work independently than with others in a group.
